Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.04,0:01:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十二話 莉娜消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.09,0:01:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人,別這樣啊\n你不可以出去阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被那個女人騎在頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒臉待在這艘船上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.73,0:01:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想成為那女人的部下\n古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.92,0:02:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是你馬士文大人的部下阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.12,0:02:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女人是坐上MS駕駛艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就興奮的失常的低俗女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是違反軍紀的人\n只要我一個就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文,安多拉就交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心的走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是普通的傳令兵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖,你說句話阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人,保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,戈圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖,連你也拋棄我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.53,0:02:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人!請回來阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.11,0:02:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文離開安多拉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈瑪哈瑪就沒人駕駛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是還有你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是不想駕駛MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是敵人有新型高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光靠薩克C是阻擋不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪與船塢艦的接觸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才困擾阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.62,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了!讓這艘船與船塢間接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以阻止亞加碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可以順便補給安多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?這是好主意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,根本就是寶山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.19,0:03:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個那個,全是值錢的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會撞上去的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我發現好東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.66,0:03:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是薩克啊\n真正的MS06F
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎都沒有壞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS-06?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那很值錢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去啊去阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.97,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要做訓練飛行了!\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.62,0:03:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過去吧,浮游物中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能有敵人的魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是捷度,改變預定計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就回去亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個薩克還能使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是預定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先去拉比安羅茲補充補給物資嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是撿垃圾的時候!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也能成為補給物資!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以賣超高價呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,別在玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子乖乖閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥你不也是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該照他們說的做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.35,0:04:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?米諾夫斯基粒子太濃,聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,那邊如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK,可以走了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他竟然假裝聽不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去負責吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.13,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必定要替哥哥負起責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你,露卡,讓我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.44,0:04:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法...我陪你去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜你沒有必要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,座位很窄的\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我代替你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不去,哥哥不會聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.89,0:05:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡...她要求出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜也在一起嗎?\n是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,每一個都那麼任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便他們吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了嗎?露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓你爸爸太困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,謝謝你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心別咬到舌頭\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡和莉娜,現在出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜你真辛苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還比不上布拉度艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.19,0:05:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼最近的孩子\n都那麼任性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.33,0:05:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家的小孩就乖多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.41,0:05:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱薩衛,珍,你們還好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是個壞爸爸阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人船塢艦進入鎖定圈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,到這裏就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始炮擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全速衝上船塢艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.99,0:06:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快反擊!\n亞加瑪還沒到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個節奏,這個震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛快阿,太痛快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加快速度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他們打爛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人...好可怕阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊,攻擊\n沖阿,沖阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的天啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C對做好出動的準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.07,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.35,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明,是你嗎?\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.51,0:07:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C隊去鎮壓船塢艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼安多拉會先抵達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得快點通知亞加瑪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個光是亞加瑪的MS嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.31,0:07:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是!露卡也坐在裏面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像被發現了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.53,0:07:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥機的駕駛員是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是露卡小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人怎麼會知道是我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.37,0:07:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了...我是古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.18,0:07:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你背叛的古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.60,0:08:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候的...?幹什麼?有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要清算上次的帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常叫我要有借有還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽?討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有戀母情結阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣妄下斷語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心吃到苦頭阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,拉比安羅茲方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有突發性的能源反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被安多拉搶先了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度先生很厲害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼好的寶物是很難找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.33,0:08:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幾個在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲受到攻擊了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們沒過去不就更好\n對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想偷懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害得莉娜代替你們去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼一回事?伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去代替捷度負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,莉娜她沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.96,0:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米諾夫斯基粒子太濃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還無法與拉比安羅茲連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.41,0:09:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,你在摸哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那薩克怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.23,0:09:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朋友跟錢哪一個重要?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說薩克比較重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,薩克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.37,0:09:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,亞加瑪全速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒空慢慢繞遠路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.34,0:09:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前進到拉比安羅茲的正面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.27,0:09:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前先處理掉薩克吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,這個薩克可以用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣...太過分了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被我抓到了吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胸口怎麼一直跳個不停?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽...莫非這個就是戀愛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手,放開手,戀母狂\n哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就去救你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明\n露卡,不要阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.78,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想抓的人是我吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她還是個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你保證放她的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就去你身邊\n露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然敢保證了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.08,0:11:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好英俊,真有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿...你好會說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明先生....\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好舊式的駕駛艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會做的太過份了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想成為那傢伙的俘虜嗎?\n不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女人竟然一再利用我的弱點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.93,0:12:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我絕不會原諒她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.85,0:12:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.03,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,我在這邊\n快點,後面有人在追截
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,我現在就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟在後面的是壞人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定密告了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.49,0:12:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是亞加瑪的援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.22,0:12:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,是亞加瑪的戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽見了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一定是與高達合體的戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.54,0:12:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有船塢艦當作盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不敢出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後在鎮壓船塢艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先把薩克C隊派去支援\n是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!你沒事吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,你趕來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查他們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣無法組合成為ZZ高達阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,還是別去吧....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都這個時候了你還說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.96,0:13:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看?\n你真的要去這麼危險的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我在這裏把你丟下去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.42,0:13:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭盔給你帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.77,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉...我以前對你這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼這麼無情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了!捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.11,0:13:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樣蒼蠅一樣飛個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我用ZZ高達收拾你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,露卡,去吧\n知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C隊,阻止他們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被他們合體就危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡是哪一個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像很喜歡你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.90,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,撐到亞加瑪抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達就可以出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經修好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只做了應急措施\n應該還可以用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.27,0:14:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,拜託你了\n伊萊,別太免強 知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把Z高達維修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出動...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣算什麼Z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心被自己人的槍彈打中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.99,0:14:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉的MS裏頭沒有薩克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你告訴捷度他們\n我坐Z薩克過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,Z薩克過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別當成敵人攻擊阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼畫面阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有360度螢幕阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.66,0:15:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是敵人剛好處在框框位置\n我就看不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甩不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊?吉翁的薩克?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體是Z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看清楚了沒,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是Z高達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼裝上那個頭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.05,0:15:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是我不應該來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想攻擊底部核戰機...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼敵人一再出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.14,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜,太好了,你沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有我跟在旁邊當然不必擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是Z高達的頭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就沒別的辦法修理嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這MS愈看愈噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就一起消滅掉吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,快合體成ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.28,0:16:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家去吧,聽見了嗎!\n聽見了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,底部核戰機準備完畢OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頂部核戰機OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.80,0:16:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ㄟ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.95,0:16:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.59,0:16:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別背對敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.67,0:17:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,媽媽\n請以代代相傳的榮耀之名保護我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量差太遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.49,0:17:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你想殺死我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.48,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼會在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是我們想問的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開吧!\n不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈哈哈...下一個是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不行了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想吐阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.37,0:17:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人...薩克C隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵不過ZZ高達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.44,0:17:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必要時把船塢艦當人質就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船塢艦飛到本艦頭上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.61,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人...\n這樣下去會被壓扁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.81,0:18:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!用逆噴射甩開他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開我的MS去攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人...請穿太空衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿上那種不透氣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就感受不到戰場的氣氛了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑ZZ高達的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,足可摧毀一整艘戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.47,0:18:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為身體大就一定贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人,敵人阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸口快撕裂了,好痛快阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個MS是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意製造破綻誘使我上當嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真難纏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.16,0:18:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在跳吧,在跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.06,0:18:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有感覺到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是靈魂\n在宇宙奔馳的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.64,0:19:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,你在胡說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙飛過來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳燿的很快樂的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我會看到剛才的景色?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.68,0:19:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是怎麼了?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一動也不動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是變型太複雜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使他無法動彈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n哥哥,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,你怎麼了?振作點阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,他昏過去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭小鬼,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.88,0:19:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那架MS是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.80,0:20:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個解決掉你,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什...什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一下子就力量減低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射劍也使不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機,快動阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.59,0:20:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,你二度背叛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我卻又忍不助救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明,你弄錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.10,0:20:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快動阿,核戰機,可惡,這破東西!\n莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.70,0:20:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C隊就出姬娜大人後回艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.14,0:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,安多拉逃了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉哪呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.85,0:21:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡應該和她在一起\n莉娜呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.32,0:21:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ㄟ..!你說莉娜怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.52,0:21:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他被拋出核戰機了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!是露卡...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,莉娜怎麼不見了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,捷度,莉娜她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她被安多拉的MS帶走了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.69,0:21:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.19,0:21:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉跑往哪裏去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏?躲在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有太多假隕石\n跟米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.20,0:22:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦跟掉了就很難找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.89,0:22:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼不是露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.15,0:22:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷腦筋\n這麼小的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.51,0:22:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!\n我太粗心了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.11,0:22:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到哪裏去了?莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒙德和比查似乎又在策劃著什麼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.60,0:23:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想努力奪回莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.06,0:23:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長 因為慎重就把我關起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.33,0:23:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該正好相反才對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.33,0:23:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才讓敵人佔了先機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.87,0:24:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核心戰機分離後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.71,0:24:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就應該期待我的活躍了 看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.14,0:24:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.54,0:24:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妹妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.87,0:24:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的眼淚只會給一個人看見

